{"tid":1589534,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"收音機舊日伴隨自己","createTime":"2019-09-23T10:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T15:20:43.000Z","uid":182519,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f230abe14af55420aaa38277e7dbfc5a2f3165","tid":1589534,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"收音機舊日伴隨自己 <br />\n何日風再起 (梅姐嘅何日，同我最愛嘅哥哥嘅風再起時）<br />\n九七初大膽預言這裡 <br />\n未來滿希冀<br />\n但到一定年紀 <br />\n回看這 回歸變天 （要再霖下，好似有啲怪）<br />\n放下稚氣 <br />\n哭中帶悲 <br />\n<br />\n歌與影大熱漸成歷史 <br />\n彷彿幾世紀 <br />\n黑色衣附著舊時夢想 <br />\n看淡生與死 <br />\n曾為生活而放棄 <br />\n不擇手段贏盡厚利 <br />\n世界是大人遊戲 <br />\n那幼稚童年誰僅記<br />\n......<br />\n時代革命這口號 <br />\n有哪個堅守擁抱"},{"pid":"ebaa6e7fd8d51dc76d1fe5ff6aeef147269aabd3","tid":1589534,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"無傷悲<br />\n留給你"},{"pid":"eb700366089ae4f62b5cc463ffb9f0088528b390","tid":1589534,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:49:55.000Z","msg":"世界有太多廢老"},{"pid":"0c6f91da0e6d790ee52e6a93bb09efab270dfc89","tid":1589534,"uid":205534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"唔啱音"},{"pid":"68287ee894f377a41cc6f00debfa30d953451002","tid":1589534,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:20:43.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？"}]}